WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
A domain registered for ten years with no published mail policy.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
No SPF. No DMARC. No Null MX record.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Without these controls, any domain becomes a free spoofing vector.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Reputation systems do not distinguish between negligence and compromise.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
They only see the absence of published policy.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
This domain was exposed for a decade — without anyone noticing.
